desc: [Coming Spring 2022] We are excited to open Kelowna's newest speciality grocery store on 1095 Ellis St. Located next to Central Kitchen! Sign up to our newsletter for updates as we get closer to our opening date!

layout.text:
Stocking foods from around the world, fresh produce & meats, grocery basics, cafe eats and more. Ellis Street Market is your one-stop grocery store in Kelowna’s North End. 
Get updates for what’s to come and our opening day by signing up for our newsletter!
